        <h2 class="card-title">Welcome to Ultimate Frisbee Scorigami</h2>
        <p class="card-text">
          This web application visualizes Ultimate Frisbee game statistics with a focus on "scorigami" - 
          the tracking of unique score combinations that have occurred in games.
        </p>
