<div class="row mt-4">
  <div class="col-12">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h3 class="card-title">What is Scorigami?</h3>
        <p class="card-text">
          Scorigami is a concept originally created by Jon Bois for NFL football, tracking unique score combinations 
          that have occurred in games. This project applies the same concept to Ultimate Frisbee.
        </p>
        <p class="card-text">
          Each cell in the scorigami chart represents a possible score combination, with the home team score on the 
          vertical axis and the away team score on the horizontal axis. Colored cells indicate score combinations 
          that have occurred in games, with the color representing the home team.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
